title: Variation of mass distributions of U238 fission fragments with neutron energy

x4codes.shortRef: Jour: Soviet Journal of Nuclear Physics, Vol.6, p.331 (1968)

x4freetext: Variation of mass distributions of U238 fission
U(3)O(8) as U-238 sample, U-235 content about 0.1%.
a - level density coefficient for excitation of FF pair
E-EXC`` - excitation energy at available for FF before
Subents 007-010 were added ( data from article).
Source of data (Subents 003,006) is not clear.
